00194     int rv;

00207   std::string getOrder() {
00208     std::string val;
00209     int rv;
00210 
00211     rv=m_tsv.getHeader("order",val);
00212     if(rv==TSV_OK) {
00213       Err::check(val.compare("row_major")==0 || val.compare("col_major")==0, "order header in clf file must be set to 'row_major' or 'col_major'");
00214       return val;
